                        </Text>
                        <Text strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="The impacts of tourism have negatively affected lots of aspects in this area of Peru. Many of the people that are actually benefitting from tourism are not from the local area, which is causing local businesses and the community to have a poorer quality of life. This then leads to increases in civil unrest, crime and inequality. " wrappingWidth="370.2812042236328">
                           <font>
                              <Font name="Century Gothic" size="13.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="     Two of the main challenges that Piedritas faces is deforestation and environmental degradation in order to build a sustainable ecotourism industry. To address these issues, Ecoswell has implemented, with support from energy company Enel, the &quot;Green Piedritas&quot; Environmental Education and Community Ecotourism Project. This is to educate the community on the harmful impacts of producing charcol and implementing initiatives to preserve the local ecosystem." wrappingWidth="369.9464111328125">
                           <font>
