                           </font>
                           <VBox.margin>
                              <Insets bottom="5.0" />
                           </VBox.margin>
                        </Text>
                        <Text strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="Sanitation" underline="true">
                           <font>
                              <Font name="Century Gothic" size="13.0" />
                           </font>
                           <VBox.margin>
                              <Insets right="307.0" />
                           </VBox.margin>
                        </Text>
                        <Text strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="In Lobitos, the majority of homes are connected to the collapsed sewer line, which is polluting the local area. This overflow is present as pools of wastewater which create health hazards, unpleasent sights, smells and pollution to the local environment. Many households do build their own soakaways but with few other available options, people often resort to open defacation." wrappingWidth="370.44630432128906">
                           <font>
                              <Font name="Century Gothic" size="13.0" />
                           </font>
                        </Text>
                        <Text strokeType="OUTSIDE" strokeWidth="0.0" text="     Ecoswell has put in place some pilot projects to deal with the sanitation problems. These include a dry composting toilet unit. It saves more than 15,000 litres of water and can produce close to 2,000 litres of high-grade compost per year. They have also installed two 300W PV panels and a 7,000 litre biodigester which has a capacity for primary treatment of sewage before it filters safely into the ground." wrappingWidth="370.59271335601807">
